<h2>Account Deletion Information</h2>

<p>
Users can permanently delete their LightX VPN account directly from the application.
</p>

<h3>How to Delete Your Account</h3>
<ol>
    <li>Open the LightX VPN application.</li>
    <li>Go to the Profile or Account Settings section.</li>
    <li>Select <strong>Delete Account</strong>.</li>
    <li>Confirm the deletion request.</li>
    <li>Your account deletion request will be processed and your account will be permanently removed.</li>
</ol>

<h3>Data That Will Be Deleted</h3>
<p>
When an account is deleted, the following information is permanently removed:
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Account information</li>
    <li>Email address (if provided)</li>
    <li>Authentication and login records associated with the account</li>
    <li>User preferences and settings</li>
    <li>VPN usage information linked to the account</li>
    <li>Any other personal data associated with the account</li>
</ul>

<h3>Data Retention</h3>
<p>
Account deletion requests are processed promptly. Personal account data is permanently deleted within 30 days of the deletion request.
</p>

<p>
Certain information may be retained for a limited period if required for legal compliance, fraud prevention, security investigations, dispute resolution, or enforcement of our terms and policies.
</p>

